  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Superior Rooms </strong>sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They're a spacious 28m² and have a balcony and a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Twin Deluxe Rooms</strong> are 35m² and have a bath and shower. They can sleep up to four using a double sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Twin Prestige Rooms </strong>are 45m² and have a bath and shower as well as a lounge area with a double sofa bed. They are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Spa Suites</strong> are 45m² and available for couples. Enjoy a private infrared sauna, 2 seat jacuzzi, tisana corner, seating area with log fire and a spacious balcony with views of the valley. This room can be requested for 1 or 2 nights at the start or end of your holiday. Available on request - please call to enquire. </p>
